    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Clothes or draperies customarily indicative of bereavement, often donned during a period designated for the conventional or ceremonial manifestation of sorrow.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
